{"tid":2272150,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 奪回歸後首冠　向定延溫馨喊話「我們愛妳！」","createTime":"2020-11-05T02:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T09:06:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21ea4f5439801efd77248b2d800f2ea6e151f050","tid":2272150,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_f8060cf91dde29bff0c9fc6835b609ab/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-05/131414-883356.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_f8060cf91dde29bff0c9fc6835b609ab%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-05%2F131414-883356.png&h=9c453b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昨晚 TWICE 在回歸後首度登上《Show Champion》就抱回了冠軍獎盃，恭喜她們！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨天（4 日）在 MBC Music 播出的《Show Champion》中，TWICE 以最新主打歌 &ldquo;I Can&rsquo;t Stop Me&rdquo; 打敗 SEVENTEEN、TXT、任昌丁和張凡俊等音源強手，成為 11 月第一週的冠軍得主。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f81090fb523a8974ba6d30ecdcb58e22/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-05/131414-883355.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f81090fb523a8974ba6d30ecdcb58e22%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-05%2F131414-883355.jpeg&h=4d2f3e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獲獎後的 TWICE 一邊帶來安可表演一邊說：「謝謝 ONCE，這是我們憑 &ldquo;I Can&rsquo;t Stop Me&rdquo; 拿到的第一個第一名！」接下來也用一人一句話感謝粉絲，還不忘提到「昨天是我們敲定粉絲名 &ldquo;ONCE&rdquo; 的五週年紀念日，真的很感謝始終支持我們的 ONCE 和所有人。」並在最後向這次缺席活動的成員定延大喊「我們愛妳」！<br />\n<br />\n最後除了回味 TWICE 昨晚表演的 &ldquo;I Can&rsquo;t Stop Me&rdquo;，也不妨看看觀看次數即將破億的 MV！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment、MBC Music）"},{"pid":"6aeb13c6aaa888c69959e3e0247d752d98621a2e","tid":2272150,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face